    "title": "Gateway approval is not bound to the executed router, so callers can arm unrelated allowlisted spenders",
    "locations": [
      "onchain_auto/0x3335a88bb18fd3b6824b59af62b50ce494143333/contracts/RubicProxy.sol:66",
